commit.message:
Add instructions on managing dependency updates.

Managing dependency updates can be tricky because of the use of pinned
dependencies in `can` when used in conjuction with the package-lock.json
file. This is a new guide to explain some recommendations on remediation
when encountering these problems.
PMO: var -> let
